### Steps for installation/upgrade CRUX:
1. Boot from CDROM or USB with this image
2. Add other software if necessary: pkguse -su /media/crux pkgname ...
3. Run the installation script: setup
### Install:
1. Edit /etc/rc.conf
2. Set the root password and create user accounts
### Upgrade:
1. Check out the rejects by rejmerge
2. Update the bootloader if necessary
### Finish:
1. Reboot into the installed/upgraded system
